Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,從新月學園外出要遵守幾條規則
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去吃派 蛋糕和冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可想的都是吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:11.71,Comment,,0,0,0,,就算出了校門 你們還是新月學園的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:14.86,Comment,,0,0,0,,必須時刻保持優雅 高貴和善良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,篝同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,第一點 要作為新月學園的學生帶著榮譽行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,第二點 不許使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果魔法出了差錯 你們承擔不起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,菲內拉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,校長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,網購的長靴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,戴在頭上就變成帽子了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 你太嚴肅了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,學生們一臉好像從兩世紀前就一直站在這裡的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,校長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 阿修拉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,戴一下試試 很適合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都帶了作為護身符的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行不行 這種東西不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,校長?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,護身符必須是滿載回憶的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這是為了能夠平安歸來的護符
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要放在回來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,順便說一下 我的是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,魔杖？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要把為了它想要回來的東西放到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,讓校長看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,貼身攜帶的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看了不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要去鎮上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西說這是近路我才跟著來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這種蘑菇只有墓地才有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,墓地天狗菇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼 好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,陰森森的 感覺會有怪物蹦出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 會被詛咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,被詛咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這裡就給人這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,修復魔法的藥劑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這些是阿修拉老師教我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好歹做出來的 應該有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以 老師也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,校外禁止使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在這種地方使用不會暴露的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 如果出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂你真是的 擔心過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是亞可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sosomme Tidiare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看你做的好事 蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而且墓碑並沒有恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,詛咒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,遲鈍？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會 我的速度不會輸給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以那傢伙也馬上可以抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可恨又愚蠢的膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女嗎 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這可真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女把我復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位？ 在說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,誰來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,自己到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒死的時候就不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,現在當然也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這條命在就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,腳在 手在 頭也在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有帽子 竟然沒有帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我要讓那傢伙和這座墓碑一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,被我一刀砍碎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,去復仇啦 去復仇啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,放那傢伙跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可的魔法和蘇西的蘑菇混合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,讓埋在地下的人復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說讓死人復活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是很不妙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Foraen Mugrowna
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,做得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,能量用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,給我跑起來啊 蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,墓地天狗菇的效果只能維持到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他可能會在日落前襲擊別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,復活死人會有什麼下場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,會受到最痛苦可怕的懲罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,比這個還要痛苦可怕100倍的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎怎怎怎怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要趕緊抓到他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是個死人 怎麼跑這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不會是他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,阻阻阻阻阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是魔女小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙可能是那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你連要找的人是誰都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了就能想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,死了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 回墓地裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要是把大叔復活的事暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就要下地獄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,還是復仇更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是我們讓你復活的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你就稍微聽我們的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,街頭表演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對 這是街頭表演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,各位先生 各位女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你們現在看到的是千年一遇的驚人奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,為了手刃可恨的男人而從九泉之下復活的中世紀騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,站在我右邊的是魔女少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,為了解除男人身上的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,從九泉追隨至此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果各位覺得吃驚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,請將你們的心意摺疊好 放入這頂帽子中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝各位惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 大叔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,找垃圾就該翻垃圾箱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然沒有發現如此簡單的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,警察叔叔阿姨 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這種嚇人的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在垃圾箱裡翻垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,市民會被嚇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 說你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快給我上車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的小年輕真不懂禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔你不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你快離開那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,又說你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺是海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺是傳說中的海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以看到箱子就忍不住打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,確認裡頭是否有寶藏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你的爺爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你快告訴他不要這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,終於走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是他做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,做得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,膽敢偷東西 那兩人真不知羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你們終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 這個人太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,想起什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,記憶就藏在腦子的某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,兩小時後大家都會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,卡里班大道3號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,又要跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,更容易搬回墓地了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,變回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐 你沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒受傷 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女是睿智的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,人類的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這是常識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有急事 先行一步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那個男人的家就在卡里班大道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙的家就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那就確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.69,Comment,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你們認識這戶人家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,家裡的東西都被那家店鋪回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法道具店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是魔法黃金時期的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我們店回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法黃金期？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你上課有認真在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大約200年前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女狩獵和工業革命之間的這段時期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因為沒有機器 凡事都要靠魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這在魔法史課上已經示範過一遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那件軍裝我們也可以買下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這傢伙 和他的妻子 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,卡里班大道3號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這是剛才的地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,新月學園寄出的信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,致米蘭達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,米蘭達是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 這個嬰兒叫米蘭達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這個男人把不幸帶給了嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,區區人類 竟然和魔女相愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還私奔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真美好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一點都不美好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,妻子生下米蘭達不久後就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,男人向妻子的一族發了誓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,會把孩子培養成一位出色的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,鍾在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙是敲鐘人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙違背了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,把孩子送到學校後就再也沒和她見過面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,米蘭達孤零零一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我饒不了那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 饒不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,絕饒不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的插圖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,全民偶像真讓人懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,校長您的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道現在還在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,已經是很久之前的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,去外面走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個傻瓜膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看了這景色 再不開心的事都能拋到腦後了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,下地獄也能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這個鐘已經沒在用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面的那個已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,敲鐘的棒子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:32.61,Comment,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,又傻又蠢又無情的卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那個男人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我痛恨的人就是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,米蘭達是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子以前經常在這裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在她被學校錄取的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,用這鐘裡的棒子做了根魔杖給她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話就算分開也不會寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是一根兼具護身符作用的魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,然而我卻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,眼淚都流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是眼淚 還是綠色的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嚇到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,校長！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,米蘭達是校長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到過校長的魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,魔杖上刻著同樣的花紋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,去新月學園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟讓你復活的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你白死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,已經來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可 你在做什…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sosomme Tidiare
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,讓開 讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,校長 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,米蘭達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽快看 是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然只剩一把骨頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 比小米蘭達還要年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有肉 看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 在爸爸再死一次之前我有句話想說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來沒有怨恨過你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,努力學習魔法 都當上校長了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,校長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 爸爸遵守了約定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Liegraviele
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很遺憾 到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了你們 我度過了美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你們 魔女小姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 有朝一日再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,為魔女的未來送上祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能剛剛吸進了些大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss篝 Miss楊森 Miss曼巴巴拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不僅在校外使用了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然還用魔法讓死者復活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你們知道會有什麼下場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,罰你們去修理備件管理室裡的掃帚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這就完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,每人都要好好反省自己的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,聽明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一輩子都做不完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,少動嘴多動手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為校長很溫柔 真是看走眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好累！手要斷掉啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到有那麼多壞掃帚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 如果用修復魔法來修的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來我好羨慕魔法黃金期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都是魔法 不覺得很棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所有事都要魔女來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我也覺得現在比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就算科學盛行 有些事還是只能靠魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,出現啦 優等生發言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個人都好無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是魔法的世界絕對很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是蘑菇的世界絕對更開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不 魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,蘑菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.19,0:22:28.97,Comment,,0,0,0,,你們不要吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,蘑菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法！

